%% MyAIStorybook - System Sequence Diagram: Idea Workshop Scenario

sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant System as :System
    
    Note over User,System: Idea Workshop Scenario (Main Success)<br/>System is treated as BLACK BOX
    
    User->>System: startWorkshop(mode)
    System-->>User: workshop_started, initial_question
    
    loop gathering requirements
        User->>System: provideInput(user_input)
        System-->>User: acknowledgment, next_question
    end
    
    User->>System: requestStoryGeneration()
    System-->>User: generated_story(title, scenes[])
    
    User->>System: endWorkshop()
    System-->>User: workshop_ended
    
    Note right of System: System guides user through<br/>interactive story ideation<br/>Collects requirements internally
